At 52, I can chain pet 5-6 earths to kill one mob in Maiden's Eye for 1% exp... takes about 6-10 minutes per kill.  Its also very dangerous because people train through all the safe spots, and no loot.<br>
<br>
Or, I can kill the right side of CoM, make 10% and 100-150pp per hour, and have complete and total saftey.<br>
<br>
I am glad I am not the only one... I figured I was missing out on some great thing because I was screwing up somewhere. <p>Moghedan Carns,<BR>
